Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveTragedy struck on Friday, July 22, at Yaba College of Technology, Lagos as a final year engineering student simply identified as Abraham passed on.
The deceased, who was the sole child of his parents, was reportedly dancing on a moving automobile to celebrate his signing out when he collapsed to the ground.
Eyewitnesses tried to resuscitate him as he lost consciousness but unfortunately, he passed away.
